description: AMUNDI US TREASURY BOND 0-1Y UCITS ETF EUR Hedged Acc seeks to replicate, as closely as possible the performance of the Bloomberg US Short Treasury hedged to EUR Index , whether the trend is rising or falling while minimizing the volatility of the di?erence between the return of the Sub-Fund and the return of the Index (the “Tracking Error”). The Sub-Fund aims to achieve a level of tracking error of the SubFund and its index that will not normally exceed 1%. For further information on index rules, please refer to the fund prospectus or KID.
name: Amundi US Treasury Bond 0-1Y UCITS ETF EUR Hedged Acc
